text: Polo Welfring (10 April 1926 - 28 January 1993) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:1993 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Esch-sur-Alzette
